The '''New Republic Trade Council''' was a sub-committee of the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]], comprised of businessbeings and [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] officials.

The goal of the New Republic Trade Council was to maintain trade and commerce in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], and ensure that ventures remained open and free.

